n:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/b078eeee-b07f-4b54-aad6-1fc8ac524e81.png\"/> là hình gì?\n",
                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2025/10/28e20498-f348-443a-8dcc-e281278bf57d.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>a) Chứng minh tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c85a7179-8058-474d-a5fe-50abce0d2dc1.png\"/> là hình chữ nhật.\n<br>Ta có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3ef7a636-f118-4279-9703-fd2f91b5d9a2.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/4722b8fb-ec36-4ce5-9a8b-c5cccdaf6c56.png\"/>\n<br>Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/180dbcd5-25b8-4313-804d-cbe8e41dfffb.png\"/> vuông tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/63ddbca9-3166-48c7-8345-0123f1defed2.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/35677c03-5904-4dd6-94ae-dc3e375dc1c3.png\"/>\n<br>Xét tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/6346d572-6e34-4b10-a7b2-d5c3ad253a43.png\"/> có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/7c41afa3-7a52-4e1a-8b96-8950731e03b4.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/6945f5a4-0022-494b-87d4-82bd7f4b322e.png\"/> là hình chữ nhật.\n<br>b) Trên tia đối của tia <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/527bc8cb-9bb5-4026-8277-1ef7faed96db.png\"/> lấy điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0827ace8-da0e-471e-ac8d-7f30173ce44b.png\"/> sao cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/9311161f-a043-41d3-9baa-169bc29950b8.png\"/> Chứng minh <img style = \"vertica